description:
Tried on DBpedia endpoint:
This query works:
select ?t
where {
    dbpedia:Barack_Obama a ?t.
    FILTER(NOT EXISTS {
        ?t a dbpedia:foo.
    })
}

This doesn't:
select ?s ?t
where {
    ?s a ?t.
    FILTER(NOT EXISTS {
        ?t a dbpedia:foo.
    })
    VALUES (?s) { (dbpedia:Barack_Obama) (dbpedia:Angela_Merkel) }
}

No results?!?
Notice how it works in this one:
select ?s ?t
where {
    ?s a ?t.
    FILTER(NOT EXISTS {
        ?t a dbpedia:foo.
    })
    VALUES (?s) { (dbpedia:Barack_Obama) }
}
